name: Darren Wilson
bio: Filmmaker, author, speaker, and I really, really love Jesus.

social_posts.post_text: Well look what just showed up. It’s been 7 years since I last released a movie I directed. This movie has been 10 years in the making. I cannot wait to unleash this sucker on the world. Big announcements coming soon…
Excited to announce that The God man will officially be in theaters around the country on June 6!  More info coming soon…

Next week I’ll be in Denver for a special presentation of my new film, The God Man. I’ll only be doing a handful of these before it hits theaters on June 6 so come out and be the first to see it if you’re in the area. This is a free event. Bring anyone you can find who needs an encounter with Jesus!
Don’t forget, this Wednesday I’ll be in the Denver area hosting a free showing of my new film that will be in theaters June 6. Come on out for an early preview and bring as many people as you can!

Heading to Denver to show The God Man for the first time ever. It’s in theaters June 6, but if you live in the area now is your chance to see it early!  7 pm Wednesday night, Rock Church in Castle Rock, CO.
Tonight’s the night!  Free sneak peek of my new film at Rock Church. Denver, Colorado Springs, come on out to see the new film almost 2 months before it hits theaters!
What an amazing night showing The God Man for the first time in Denver. We’ve got some big announcements coming soon, so stay tuned!

Detroit!! I’m heading home to the church I grew up in this Sunday night to show my new film!  Come join me in Monroe, MI to catch a sneak peek of the film almost 2 months before it’s released in theaters.
This Sunday night I’ll be in Monroe to preview my newest film. Come out and see it a month and a half ahead of its premiere in theaters!
Reminder, I’ll be showing my new film in Monroe, MI tonight (Sunday) at 7 pm. Worship starts at 6:30. Come out and join me if your in the area and see the film over a month before it hits theaters!

This Friday I’ll be in south Florida to show an early preview of my new movie. It’s free but to make sure you have a spot we encourage you to register for it as seats are going fast!  You can do that here: https://harbourchurch.churchcenter.com/registrations/events/1684965

The moment has finally come: The God Man is coming to theaters June 6th! The focus of Darren Wilson’s final film in his 6-movie saga is all about Jesus, and we need your help to pack out theaters across the country. Here is your first look at the trailer. Please share this with everyone you know, and get your tickets now before they sell out, as this will be a one-night-only event!

Don't forget to share this post with your friends and family!

I’ll be doing the final preview of The God Man at Bethel Church in Redding this Friday before the movie hits theaters on June 6 (with special guest Robby Dawkins). Due to high demand they’re asking those who want to attend to register (it’s free) to ensure you have a seat. You can do that here: https://www.bethel.com/calendar/the-god-man-film-screening #thegodmanfilm

From the movie THE GOD MAN, take a sneak peek with Rabbi Jason Sobel who being raised in a Jewish home, experienced Jesus as the true Messiah.

Tonight’s the night!  The final public showing of my new film.  If you’re in the Redding area come on out. Robby Dawkins will be leading ministry afterwards. It’s going to be wild!
Good to be back.
